data.description: Fresh and clean! All new paint interior and exterior, new carpet in bedrooms, new floors throughout main living area, new stainless-steel appliances, lots of new including the kitchen sink! This 4-bedroom, 2 bath with an office gives space to spread out. Master suite, with a large walk-in closet, walk in shower and bath tub, double sink. Private back yard offers a great view of the pond. Easy walking distance to middle school and shops, easy commute to Jacksonville to Brunswick. Minutes from Kings Bay Naval Base, schools and shopping.
